net.sf.tweety.arg.dung.parser

Class DungParser

  • java.lang.Object
    • net.sf.tweety.commons.Parser
      • net.sf.tweety.arg.dung.parser.DungParser
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    DungParserConstants

    public class DungParser
extends net.sf.tweety.commons.Parser
implements DungParserConstants
    This class implements a parser for dung argumentation theories. The BNF for dung abstract argumentation theory files is given by (start symbol is THEORY)

    THEORY ::== (EXPRESSION)*
    EXPRESSION ::== ARGUMENT | ATTACK
    ARGUMENT ::== "argument(" + ARGUMENT_NAME + ")."
    ATTACK ::== "attack(" + ARGUMENT_NAME + "," + ARGUMENT_NAME + ")."

    ARGUMENT_NAME is a sequence of symbols from {a,...,z,A,...,Z,0,...,9,_,-,(,),[,],{,},~,<,>,.} with a letter at the beginning.
